#!/bin/bash
# -*- mode: bash; tab-width: 2; -*-
# vim: ts=2 sw=2 ft=bash noet

cat <<-END
:::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::: NOT YET SUPPORTED !!!

We love erlang and would love the opportunity to support compiling and deploying
erlang apps. To be honest, we weren't sure how much demand there would be for
deploying erlang apps. Now that you're here, PLEASE TELL US about your app so we
can determine the best way to compile and deploy it!

irc   : #nanobox
email : hello@nanobox.io

::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::
END

exit 1
